# PowerEdge R630 (gen 13, 1U dual-socket).
#
# UNTESTED but high-confidence — extrapolated from R730xd (probed,
# same gen 13 / iDRAC8 BMC firmware family). R730xd's BMC clamps PWM
# below 10% to a safety RPM (no fan-stall risk); R630 expected to
# behave identically since they share the BMC firmware lineage.
#
# If you observe fan stall or BMC errors at MIN_FAN=10, bump to 20.

: "${MIN_FAN:=10}"
